quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,50,"Yamiroore amen wonaani, si wonaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hin∆īaango yiitere."
  54,51,"GooŇč…óii Min kalkiino yeradii…ďe mon. Hara wooday baajitoray…óo?"
  54,52,"Kala hu'unde nde …ďe ngolli no ka ndeer …óeri,"
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko binndaa …óum."
  54,54,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďren ngonii e Aljannaaji e caatli,"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laam…óo kattan…óo."
  55,1,"Joom yurmeende e on."
  55,2,"O anndinii alqur'aana."
  55,3,"O tagi ne…ó…óaŇčke o."
  55,4,"O anndini mo …ďanngingol.(la…ď…ďin'gol)"
  55,5,"Nayange ngen e lewru ndun [hi…ói ndogira] limoore,"
  55,6,"koode …óeen kadi e le…ó…óe …óeen, hino cujjude."
  55,7,"Kammu ngun, o toowni ngu. O wa…ói nun…óal ngal,"
  55,8,"fii wota on mbewu ka pe'esir…óe."
  55,9,"√Ďinniron petgol ngol no nun…óiri. Wata on ustu pe'esir…óe …óeen."
  55,10,"Leydi ndiin, O wa…óanndi tagoore ndeen:"
  55,11,"Muuyantee…ói hino e mayri, e le…ó…óe tamaro mar…óe po∆ī∆īi."
  55,12,"e gabbe mar…óe √Īa'ande, e uurngol."
  55,13,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óin woni ko njeddoton?"
  55,14,"O tagiri ne…ó…óo on immorde e loopal, ba'ngal e ko ju…óaa."
  55,15,"O tagiri jinnaaji …óiin, immorde e lew lewndu yiite laa…ďuki."
  55,16,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óiin njeddoton?"